This bioluminescent {POKEMON} emits ultraviolet wavelengths which stimulate vitamin D production in humans. Solarvae makes a great lamp if kept content.
Unlike the docile Solarvae, Xenofuge is hostile and temperamental. Its exoskeleton barely contains an intense source of heat, which resembles a red giant star.
